{
  "id": "adv_event_2604_01_03",
  "title": "よく\n分からない\nセンス",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、この三人でユニットを組んで\n地下闘技場の大会に出場することになったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.5819049834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 7.7819048881
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "実は大会に出るには条件があって\n歌うのはオリジナルの曲じゃないといけないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7819048881,
      "endTime": 13.4967803954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 13.6967803001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "オリジナルの楽曲……\nつまり、私達三人で歌う新曲が必要なのね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6967803001,
      "endTime": 21.3893651008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.5893650054
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "でも曲作りは難しいわよ。作詞はともかく\n作曲や編曲はプロの手を借りないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5893650054,
      "endTime": 29.2983444212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 29.4983443259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにお願いして\nいつもお世話になってる作曲家さんに依頼してみる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4983443259,
      "endTime": 34.806755733399996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.006755638
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "一応聞くけど、「どうして新曲を作りたいんだ？」って\n質問されたら、どう答えるつもり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.006755638,
      "endTime": 42.1933318136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 42.3933317183
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "「野良アイドルになった芽衣達が秘密の地下闘技場で\nなんでもありの非合法ライブに出場するためだよー」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3933317183,
      "endTime": 50.0215854643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.2215853689
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そして僕らは叱られて\n地下闘技場に行くのを禁じられるんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2215853689,
      "endTime": 55.7401843069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "えー、それは困るよ\nでも、作曲家さんに頼まないと曲作りは出来ないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7401843069,
      "endTime": 64.1663296698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 55.9589236008
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 64.3663295744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、怜のお兄さんは\nバンドをやってるんだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3663295744,
      "endTime": 68.3261482237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 68.5261481283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、『MYSELFish』っていうバンドで\n結構人気があるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5261481283,
      "endTime": 73.4598217961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……なるほど、そういうことね。バンドの曲は全部\n自作してるそうだから、頼めば曲を作ってもらえるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6598217008,
      "endTime": 84.10775852169999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 78.5400022889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりにお兄ちゃんの顔も見たいし\n近いうちに会って話してみるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3077584264,
      "endTime": 90.3863524434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.586352348
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "出来れば新曲は、今までの曲とは違う感じにしたいね\n印象が違えば僕達の正体も気付かれにくいはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.586352348,
      "endTime": 100.0356948849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.2356947895
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "今まで歌ったことがない曲かぁ……\n演歌とか、ヘビメタとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2356947895,
      "endTime": 106.71862001379999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 106.9186199184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "デスメタルもいいね。怜からお兄さんに頼んでよ\nシャウトやデスボイスを入れてくれって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9186199184,
      "endTime": 113.6460348125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 113.8460347171
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "あんまり変な要求はしないでよね\n私がお兄ちゃんに変なやつだと思われるじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.8460347171,
      "endTime": 120.3460345263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 120.546034431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、新曲は怜のお兄さんにお願いするとして\n後、必要なのはステージ衣装かな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.546034431,
      "endTime": 128.2336763377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 128.4336762423
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "デザインはやったことあるけど、芽衣達だけで\n衣装を全部手作りするのは、さすがに難しそうだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4336762423,
      "endTime": 136.8371460908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、これも作曲家さんと同じで、お世話になってる\nデザイナーさんには頼めないし……もし頼むなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0371459955,
      "endTime": 146.4608194345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 146.6608193391
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "プロのデザイナーじゃないけど衣装作りの経験があって\n私達と仲良しで秘密を守れる信頼出来る人じゃないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.6608193391,
      "endTime": 155.8749686234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 156.0749685281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "僕の知る限り、その条件を満たすのは\n千紗しかいないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.0749685281,
      "endTime": 161.4094128601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 161.6094127648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_01_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりそうなるわよね……\n千紗に衣装作りを頼めないかメッセで聞いてみるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
